          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:bg-slate-100"
        >
          预约企业培训沟通
        </a>
        <a
          href="/services"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-white/20 bg-white/5 px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-white/10"
        >
